title: kidsme Food Squeezer
description: kidsme Food Squeezer with unique holes on silicone sac is particularly designed for babies self-feeding semi-liquid or liquid food supplement such as rice and congee. In combination with the Food Feeder and Food Feeder Plus, babies can develop a rich palate and receive benefits of eating whole fresh food.
